{"tid":1761903,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"1130［老幼攜手 和你同行］ 中學生x銀髮族集會","createTime":"2019-11-29T08:10:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-30T06:14:04.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f9feabfc29289ef081d7eee27acbab7c5b94795e","tid":1761903,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T08:10:08.000Z","msg":"跨代connect! 集會內容：<br />\n<br />\n中學生與銀髮族發言：<br />\n化學系博士K Kwong<br />\n&ldquo;學凝&rdquo;學生代表<br />\nBoyz Reborn<br />\n若水忠醫<br />\n雄仔叔叔<br />\n中學生校媒代表<br />\n孫勵生（社福界)<br />\n香城書院<br />\n馬屎埔陳伯<br />\n<br />\n同場參與組織/團體：<br />\n樹窿, 心理輔導支援<br />\n紅十字會<br />\n&ldquo;18區減廢新戰線&rdquo;遊行集會回收<br />\n<br />\n[老幼攜手 和你同行」守則，保你平安！<br />\n1. 自備充足糧水、食物，櫈仔，毛巾、藥油<br />\n2. 不接受任何金錢捐獻<br />\n3. 全程Be water<br />\n<br />\n*已獲發不反對通知書<br />\n*銀髮族所有活動，均不設籌款行動及不接受任何團體組織當日前來設立任何義賣/眾籌活動<br />\n<br />\n集會詳情： <br />\n日期：2019年11月30日（星期六）<br />\n集會時間：14：00 - 17：00<br />\n集合時間：14：00<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n<br />\n原文：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/845348632510629/posts/949027942142697?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F845348632510629%2Fposts%2F949027942142697%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=GkFIyr4nU57GJWscoxyRLT2nqaxvu5zgGSEBmbQkQbg%3D&h=d033f6b6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/845348632510629/posts/949027942142697?sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"a3133c510ac4fd3899f52d8a1f047d7abca88b61","tid":1761903,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T08:10:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /